<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <title>Session Reminder</title>
</head>
<body>
    <h2>Session Reminder</h2>
    <p>This is a reminder for your upcoming <%= type === 'client' ? 'counseling' : 'client' %> session.</p>
    <p>Session starts at: <%= startTime.toLocaleString() %></p>
    <p>Please ensure you:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Have a stable internet connection</li>
        <li>Are in a quiet, private space</li>
        <li>Have tested your camera and microphone</li>
        <li>Join the session 5 minutes early</li>
    </ul>
    <p>Click the link in your dashboard to join the session when it's time.</p>
</body>
</html>